{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we developed a dual-task model for ophthalmic image analysis.",
    "Firstly, we utilized a multimodal transformer to intelligently convert FFA images into medical reports.",
    "Then, we implemented an LLM to facilitate interactive QA.",
    "Through comprehensive automated and manual evaluations, the system demonstrated reliable and satisfactory performance.",
    "This research represents the demonstration of the large language model's potential as an assistant for generating medical reports and enabling QA tasks to enhance FFA image interpretation."
  ]
}